lola , is a 1961 romantic drama film , the debut film directed by jacques demy as a tribute to director max ophüls and is described by demy as a " musical without music " .   anouk aimée starred in the title role .   the film was restored and re-released by demy 's widow , french filmmaker agnès varda .   the names of the film and title character were inspired by josef von sternberg 's 1930 film der blaue engel , in which marlene dietrich played a burlesque performer named " lola lola . "